---
title: Chicken Jalfrezi with tomato and onion raita
description: A raita is a traditional dip or side dish found in Indian cuisine. The raita in this recipe, made with tomato and onion, provides a refreshing and cooling accompaniment to the spicy chicken curry it's served alongside.
